For what value of x is the above quadrilateral a parallelogram?

x........................
6x - 25 = 2x + 15
6x = 2x + 40
4x = 40
x = 10

Check x..................
6x - 25 = 2x + 15
6(10) - 25 = 2(10) + 15
60 - 25 = 20 + 15
35 = 35

